    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. The CFD model correctly identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions with RH predictions within experimental uncertainty across all 5 operating points. The model is accepted as credible for supporting the COU decision that the CPB device hemolysis performance is acceptable relative to the predicate device.",
